### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE student_attendance (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id UUID,
    date DATE,
    status VARCHAR
);


CREATE TABLE student_performance (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id UUID,
    exam_date DATE,
    grade FLOAT,
    subject VARCHAR
);


CREATE TABLE student_progress (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id UUID,
    progress_percentage FLOAT,
    feedback TEXT
);

### STATEMENT

DELETE FROM student_progress WHERE progress_percentage < 50 AND feedback LIKE '%improve%'
